      <textAnnotation id="sid-5142449E-CE8F-4199-A6C9-1C1383926255" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Process Tower: PTP - Procure To Pay
Process Group: PM - Procure Materials and Services (Direct &amp; Indirect)
Process: PM-040-080 Assess Suppliers</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-595CBDAB-69F6-4CBF-BA47-D3676612959F" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>L3 Description-
This process is intended to ascertain suppliers' ability to consistently meet quality standard in a predictable and repeatable manner. Determine suppliers' capability to manufacture and distribute a quality product which meets the company business and commercial needs. Factors involved in this assessment include the supplier's production capacity, location, business technology environment, financial strength, percentage of business.</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-3EBBCA41-D001-4AB6-B6F0-7751A85BDB7F" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Utilize scoring data based on Ariba supplier quotation</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-E99D49E2-EEF9-4D3F-9294-7AFA723D0576" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Approval process is defined by commodity.  Ex:  For all manufacturing related items, Approved xCCB whitepaper or PRQ</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-B5DEB201-925B-4548-A06B-715CCA6560C3" signavio:alignment="left">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioDictionaryLink propertyId="name">
               <signavio:dictionaryLink>/glossary/379d0e2ec2f943cab5c10dc3521829f3</signavio:dictionaryLink>
            </signavio:signavioDictionaryLink>
            <signavio:signavioType dataObjectType="IT-System"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bgcolor" metaValue="#e1e1e1"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>SAP Ariba</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-2F06F06F-F426-459C-A3C3-A5F8643FED89" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Making an assessment based on set criteria</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-08927DD8-7055-40D3-8983-D546F8270800" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel bold="" fill="#ff0000" fontFamily="" fontSize="" italic="" ref="text-left"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel bold="" fill="#ff0000" fontFamily="" fontSize="" italic="" ref="text-right"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Flow has been migrated to BIC. Please inform the process steward Dhanwantry, Kalyan R &lt;kalyan.r.dhanwantry@intel.com&gt; and BPM Champions D'Elia, Traci &lt;traci.delia@intel.com&gt;,Newman, Jennifer &lt;jennifer.newman@intel.com&gt;of any design changes that occur within the flow moving forward. This will enable us to reflect those changes in the BIC and WIKI business process documentation.</text>
      </textAnnotation>
   </process>
